Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Disable the Microsoft Keyboard Emoji key (scan code E01F)
; After applying this, the key will do nothing
; Then you can use SharpKeys or another tool to remap it

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Keyboard Layout]
"Scancode Map"=hex:00,00,00,00,00,00,00,00,02,00,00,00,00,00,1f,e0,00,00,00,00
